41:19.553 --> 41:21.688
Have some. I have so much,
it's not even funny.

41:21.793 --> 41:22.838
Come on.

41:25.192 --> 41:26.192
Home-made.

41:29.633 --> 41:30.633
Right? I

41:45.043 --> 41:48.768
My lady. Wow. Such a gentleman.

41:48.863 --> 41:50.768
Thank you. Watch your step here.

41:50.863 --> 41:52.838
Thanks for driving, Isobel.

41:54.192 --> 41:55.192
Thanks.

41:56.793 --> 41:58.558
I can take these. Oh.

41:59.993 --> 42:02.353
I always wondered what this place
looked like on the inside.

42:04.272 --> 42:05.768
What do you mean?

42:05.963 --> 42:09.088
Oh, I hung out in the neighborhood a
lot, but I've always loved this house.

42:10.353 --> 42:11.353
Really?

42:11.392 --> 42:13.367
I wonder if we ever played together
as kids.

42:18.043 --> 42:19.328
I'm sure we did.

42:23.142 --> 42:24.658
Hey! You're home!

42:24.753 --> 42:25.753
Dad!

42:27.833 --> 42:31.728
You must be this Cole that
Sarah's been talking about.

42:31.833 --> 42:33.768
I'm Alan. Nice to meet you.

42:33.863 --> 42:35.167
Pleasure to meet you, sir.

42:38.353 --> 42:41.968
Well, thank you for today.
Yeah. Should probably get going.

42:42.113 --> 42:45.018
OK. Don't forget about our plans
for tomorrow.

42:45.142 --> 42:48.297
Oh, never. As soon as the sun comes
up, I'll be right here.

42:48.392 --> 42:49.808
OK. I'll make coffee.

42:52.072 --> 42:53.198
Bye.

43:02.223 --> 43:03.888
What? A whole year?

43:04.033 --> 43:06.528
In Europe? Yeah. Isn't that
the best story?

43:06.633 --> 43:08.198
Man, I wish I could do that.

43:09.473 --> 43:11.808
Look, I know that your whole life
here, but...

43:11.942 --> 43:14.297
You know it's not
going anywhere, right?

43:14.322 --> 43:17.888
All I'm saying is, I don't want you
to wait to fulfill your dreams.

43:18.033 --> 43:21.528
You know, if you wait in one spot
too long, you can get stuck.

43:21.633 --> 43:22.808
Trust me. I

