Hey, I didn't know that you
and your dad sold furniture.

43:27.142 --> 43:28.917
Yeah. Well, my dad does
most of the work.

43:29.072 --> 43:32.088
My mom used to help him so I just
pitch in where I can.

43:32.223 --> 43:34.558
